---
title: Asian-Style Double Beef & Ponzu Carrot Noodles with Crushed Peanuts
description: A slaw bowl with tender beef on top already sounds like a winning dinner, but we think we can go a step further. Sweet garlicky flavours for the beef and a sticky ponzu sauce for the slaw. Seal the deal by drizzling over a sesame dressing
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6604f02afaa50670154dc0cd-761a8e68.jpeg
